# Streamlit App Walkthrough (Labels & Fixes)

## Summary
The piano now includes visible key labels on the keys themselves.

## New Features
- **Key Labels**: The note names (C, D, E, F, G, A, B) are drawn directly on the corresponding keys.
- **Improved Visibility**: Labels are in high-contrast red for easy reading.

## How to Run
```bash
./.venv/bin/streamlit run app.py
```
Open the URL shown in the terminal (usually http://localhost:8501).
